# Code used for master thesis Information Science of the University of Groningen, the code is generated by Claude and adapted where necessary by the author.
# The code classifies BOA registrations from the Gemeente Groningen in nine different classes, comparing one SVM, seven encoders and four decoders.
# Dutch-specific encoders: BERTje, Geotrend NL-BERT, RobBERT v2 and RobBERT 2023. 
# Multilingual encoders: mBERT, mDeBERTa v3 and XLM-RoBERTa. 
# Dutch-specific decoders: Fietje-2b and GPT-2 Small Dutch.
# Multilingual decoders: OPT-13B and Qwen2.5-0.5B.
# The dataset is not publicly available.
